Terms of Sale:

Books are offered if unsold. We try to describe the state of the books precisely. Minor defects such as a

name on first page, ex libris stamp, minimal wear or annotations are not always mentioned.

Orders can be done via email (info@thelandofnod.be) or in writing, not by telephone.

Shipping costs are based on books weighing 2.2 LB, or 1 KG. If your book order is heavy or oversized, we may contact you to let you know extra shipping is required.
